  <scopecontent id="aspace_f134a32deb3f9a93b1bc552adcbcd3dd">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Collection consists primarily of Cornell diplomas from alumni, but also includes some Cornell certificates and non-Cornell certificates/diplomas from alumni.</p><p> Also, some empty mailing tubes and the bottom piece of a February 8, 1922 diploma.</p>  </scopecontent>
